// VARUNA BUOY — ESP32-S3 SENSOR BRAIN FIRMWARE
// ============================================================================
// Complete autonomous flood detection system
// No WiFi, no HTTP, no Firebase — pure edge sensing
// Outputs 39-field CSV on GPIO 14 (software UART to C3)
// Receives config commands from C3 on Serial2 (GPIO 43/44)
// Receives debug commands from USB Serial
// ============================================================================

